{"tid":428700,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"你地打機要Surround效果，聽後面來既聲，係咪一定用headset?","createTime":"2017-10-08T09:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T15:37:22.000Z","uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"230b851902b14093a4aa33148d62fbf4aaafb42c","tid":428700,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:31:22.000Z","msg":"房間打機係咪多數用headset，而唔係5.1/7.1 speaker組合？<br />\n<br />\n5.1/7.1 speaker組合  好多隻喇叭，好多線，香港既書房多數放唔到好好睇睇<br />\n得返5.1/7.1 headset，好似無得揀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申︰買左Creative BlasterX Katana 2日，重試緊佢個聲"},{"pid":"78c93669529b26daf01d4d88b048307c13229ced","tid":428700,"uid":16567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:32:18.000Z","msg":"裝喇叭係櫈背"},{"pid":"a4323a1397d99a8e6e1c4ade936a22a94a305b5c","tid":428700,"uid":22817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裝喇叭係櫈背</blockquote><br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64cbdc4228eae14f34192d77be3d47e280199c0","tid":428700,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b32ce9b08ef700e59877bcc88e318decceddbf6b","tid":428700,"uid":22817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>裝喇叭係櫈背</blockquote><br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n右呢？</blockquote><br />\n比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d2011844add417e714816596334a35568de11c","tid":428700,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>裝喇叭係櫈背</blockquote><br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n右呢？</blockquote><br />\non9"},{"pid":"d6a253ce9fbc8f0041916bf41c071e8435715cda