2cba5628577a67b00c78b99","tid":428700,"uid":108421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>房間打機係咪多數用headset，而唔係5.1/7.1 speaker組合？<br />\n<br />\n5.1/7.1 speaker組合  好多隻喇叭，好多線，香港既書房多數放唔到好好睇睇<br />\n得返5.1/7.1 headset，好似無得揀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申︰買左Creative BlasterX Katana 2日，重試緊佢個聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我房仔冇位都照諗計set 5.1 speaker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n两種都用過,幾舊水買set 5.1都贏哂<br />\n耳機聲太焗,效果差好遠,戴耐又唔舒服</blockquote><br />\n兩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返去啦你"},{"pid":"4d8c057078c556593c5d4653bdfb75acd53cb435","tid":428700,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"耳機一定係最方便⋯⋯其實set 5.1都唔洗話地方大，但真係要有心機研究擺位同執線"},{"pid":"188c47476ead05d7f1ae2064a760c35198863582","tid":428700,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"擰轉頭"},{"pid":"5882977e80da458d346ee25452c2074330f6995c","tid":428700,"uid":54684,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"玩左幾日Creative BlasterX Katana<br />\n<img src=\"https://origincdn.azureedge.net/images/products/icons/image_2fc3001f-239f-41cb-af02-739241b39075.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forigincdn.azureedge.net%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Ficons%2Fimage_2fc3001f-239f-41cb-af02-739241b39075.png&h=a31f63aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都幾肯定佢無rear channels<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好話5.1  個Virtual 7.1就算有  都係好難察覺<br />\n用左battlefield 1試<br />\n又用D Dolby 7.1 samples播出來試<br />\n個Virtual 7.1唔可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Marketing gimmick<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過你前面個150~180度   佢就做得幾好   無咩令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n物體遠近 / 移動無問題<br />\n個聲真係幾震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有up firing midbass<br />\n爆炸 / 遠近 都好勁<br />\n用Battlefield 1模式, 再搖控較Bass+2~+4   聲音較12~15已經幾勁<br />\n打Battlefield 1 個場面會好宏大  好震  張枱都震埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afdbf05e813d078f96dfe403212f701e058d624","tid":428700,"uid":28168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩左幾日Creative BlasterX Katana<br />\n<img src=\"https://origincdn.azureedge.net/images/products/icons/image_2fc3001f-239f-41cb-af02-739241b39075.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forigincdn.azureedge.net%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Ficons%2Fimage_2fc3001f-239f-41cb-af02-739241b39075.png&h=a31f63aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都幾肯定佢無rear channels<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好話5.1  個Virtual 7.1就算有  都係好難察覺<br />\n用左battlefield 1試<br />\n又用D Dolby 7.1 samples播出來試<br />\n個Virtual 7.1唔可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Marketing gimmick<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過你前面個150~180度   佢就做得幾好   無咩令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n物體遠近 / 移動無問題<br />\n個聲真係幾震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有up firing midbass<br />\n爆炸 / 遠近 都好勁<br />\n用Battlefield 1模式, 再搖控較Bass+2~+4   聲音較12~15已經幾勁<br />\n打Battlefield 1 個場面會好宏大  好震  張枱都震埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打set up位两側同後面有冇墻？<br />\n呢類sound bar 反射墻都幾重要, 空間又唔可以太大<br />\n反射聲會虛啲但未至於冇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4dda4ca40d9b5bb3f23a93a60dbcde2e80359f","tid":428700,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>耳機一定係最方便⋯⋯其實set 5.1都唔洗話地方大，<span style=\"color: red;\">但真係要有心機研究擺位同執線</span></blockquote><br />\n真"},{"pid":"26cc4c9102db350a055f0e69c0b6a8a2e195883b","tid":428700,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>耳機一定係最方便⋯⋯其實set 5.1都唔洗話地方大，<span style=\"color: red;\">但真係要有心機研究擺位同執線</span></blockquote><br />\n真</blockquote><br />\n真<br />\n其實香港呢D咁既居住環境<br />\n好難全面咁玩5.1, 7.1<br />\n要視乎有無彩數   屋企間格如何<br />\n<br />\n書房就想7.1 Dolby打機？香港D樓咁細，都幾難<br />\n<br />\nSpeaker組合一地都係線，要諗好多收藏線既方法，重有點擺放？<br />\nSoundbar靠反彈，一係難做到 一係soundbar好貴<br />\n耳機就最近磅   無視環境直接打音波入耳   但打機耐D耳仔會好易焗住<br />\n<br />\nAsus Centurion 7.1囉  但又話重"},{"pid":"7fd385b91377ef4f756e1184921f769a9e64bf7b","tid":428700,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩左幾日Creative BlasterX Katana<br />\n<img src=\"https://origincdn.azureedge.net/images/products/icons/image_2fc3001f-239f-41cb-af02-739241b39075.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forigincdn.azureedge.net%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Ficons%2Fimage_2fc3001f-239f-41cb-af02-739241b39075.png&h=a31f63aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都幾肯定佢無rear channels<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好話5.1  個Virtual 7.1就算有  都係好難察覺<br />\n用左battlefield 1試<br />\n又用D Dolby 7.1 samples播出來試<br />\n個Virtual 7.1唔可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Marketing gimmick<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過你前面個150~180度   佢就做得幾好   無咩令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n物體遠近 / 移動無問題<br />\n個聲真係幾震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有up firing midbass<br />\n爆炸 / 遠近 都好勁<br />\n用Battlefield 1模式, 再搖控較Bass+2~+4   聲音較12~15已經幾勁<br />\n打Battlefield 1 個場面會好宏大  好震  張枱都震埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打set up位两側同後面有冇墻？<br />\n呢類sound bar 反射墻都幾重要, 空間又唔可以太大<br />\n反射聲會虛啲但未至於冇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n後面都清左好多野，基本上直接就係牆，但唔係一大幅，係凸字型中間凸出<br />\nrear channels 難feel到囉  真係無乜感覺<br />\n但前方感覺就好震撼  枱都震埋<br />\n<br />\n好多人成日推Bose Companion 5  又話有Surround又話好勁  成3千蚊<br />\n官方都只係話扮5.1   邊有全面Surround?<br />\n有無巴打報告下  Bose Companion 5有無聽到rear channels   我唔係好信"}]}